{
  "stem": "5810.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was just a child, so it was put into kind of a false seam in a-- in a shirt that I was wearing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had this money, which was gold coins, because Belgian money didn't mean anything at that point anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a lot of Jews were switching over their monies to gold coins, which could be exchanged anywhere, I guess.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was sewn in-- in my shirt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But what happened is they, for some reason, questioned the older brothers and sister first.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I guess they didn't think that anything was happening with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And every time they questioned and searched a brother or a sister, they were sent back and put back next to us, next to the-- next to my brothers and sister who hadn't been searched.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I do remember my brother being searched, coming back into the room, standing next to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother went-- was the next person to be interrogated by this Gestapo officer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went right in front of him in the line-- in his line of vision.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while she was talking to him-- I'll never forget that-- she made a gesture like this, which was meant for my brother to take whatever I was hiding, and take it and put it on himself, since he had been searched.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's exactly what he did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While this was happening and the officer was very, very involved in questioning of my mother, he went into the back and pulled out the tubes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't-- not plastic at the time, but whatever it was in, the gold coins.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he took it and put it in his pockets, since he had been searched.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
